780e461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F014459_9bc7e2ca81b777ed5b669df3c780e461.jpg&h=0d5942a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/014510_9ec2125cb233a8137eb8c2e8652bbbd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F014510_9ec2125cb233a8137eb8c2e8652bbbd0.jpg&h=a8ba0fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老母當年努力工作唔享受唔買新衫然後買到樓，所以而家成日都比佢屌亂買野亂洗錢，但我只不過係唔自己煮lunch 出去食，得閒淘下寶，買多對鞋佢都屌屌聲。<br />\n話我咁落去點買到樓，佢都都唔化嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1904ff53bebbb5f7744b74b948003a91aecdfa","tid":386270,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"以前你肯做就買到屋住<br />\n不過以前輪公屋快同租樓平<br />\n啲人寧願拎去食左佢都唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a8cf4514efd58dbe17e961ede498ed55a4ae5f","tid":386270,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前你肯做就買到屋住<br />\n不過以前輪公屋快同租樓平<br />\n啲人寧願拎去食左佢都唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個時又真係好難知道會變成今日咁既<br />\n但係今時今日仲用以前我乜乜柒柒都買到樓啦依家啲90後真係廢青咁既思想就真係好落後囉"},{"pid":"da1ab32d647c32288cd8b0b3dd098c43aa226bf8","tid":386270,"uid":86716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T18:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前你肯做就買到屋住<br />\n不過以前輪公屋快同租樓平<br />\n啲人寧願拎去食左佢都唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個時又真係好難知道會變成今日咁既<br />\n但係今時今日仲用以前我乜乜柒柒都買到樓啦依家啲90後真係廢青咁既思想就真係好落後囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個時我阿媽話已經預知到會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢仲屌我而家唔努力儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}